      <li>SEO-sensitive production environment</li>
      <li>Performance improvements without visual regressions</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- SOLUTION -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-12">
    <h2>The Solution</h2>
    <p>
      I refactored key UI components, improved layout stability, and optimized
      asset loading to enhance both performance and maintainability.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- TECHNICAL HIGHLIGHTS -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-12">
    <h2>Technical Highlights</h2>
